r />\n又話要分柝型勢<br />\n<br />\n大佬啊，我毅進仔咋，點同一時間處理咁多野<br />\n<br />\n好煩，壓力好大，六九遊行，都係不了</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1190576/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1190576/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/AwtAz1F.png\" />"},{"pid":"368519d0dc39b2d5ae6d7be6c88cabcb5811e970","tid":1792849,"uid":267007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:19:52.000Z","msg":"善用不推文回覆<br />\n<br />\nbtw dllm blocked <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966ec883a15b514e972eefaef697947ff63d2ae3","tid":1792849,"uid":51615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:20:01.000Z","msg":"唔好再劇透啦，好嗎"},{"pid":"a81b0d0a97469cbbbc3f96fcf49509d8727e8519","tid":1792849,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"樓主<br />\n葉問生cancer死左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00b57326112b5bb5b64a81a65bf3b4398083bbf","tid":1792849,"uid":7555,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"966ec883a15b514e972eefaef697947ff63d2ae3","tid":1792849,"uid":51615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:20:01.000Z","msg":"唔好再劇透啦，好嗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"Ok<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f25398fc6c71b6cb14031a59f2f1bfec4f2202e","tid":1792849,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"五毛咁早就開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91e3297d4a99050a725141470b59dac882445fa","tid":1792849,"uid":187226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"